description: A man is sleeping on a bar counter. A funny face has been drawn on his bald head. A slogan reads: “Be the artist not the canvas”
A women is kneeling in front of a toilet bowl and resting her head in her hands. A slogan reads: “12:32 AM She’s got a date with a porcelain prince.”
Several empty or half empty glasses of red wine are visible. A slogan reads: “Who decides when you’ve got enough? You or your friends?”
A woman is hanging over a toilet bowl, possibly throwing up. A slogan reads: “She thought turning down a drink would make her look bad.”
A glass of alcohol is visible in the background. A slogan reads: “Looking after a mate doesn’t always mean buying them more drinks.”
A man in a half opened button down shirt is sleeping standing up at a bus stop with a beer bottle in his hands. A slogan reads: “His mate bought the last round. But he’s paying for it.”

A man is standing bent over in a dark alley, possibly throwing up. His head is replaced by a glass he is “emptying” into the street. A slogan reads: “The more you binge drink, the more likely you are to be arrested.”

Two man are fighting in a bar. One is lying on the ground. The other is grabbing his head and is about to punch the first man. A women is holding the arm of the second man to stop him from throwing the punch. The heads of all there characters are replaced by half full alcohol glasses. The glass of the man on the ground is broken from prior punches.

The front and back sides of a coaster are shown. The front says: “Fuck off”. The back says: “If someone’s pressuring you to have another drink calmly slide this coaster over to them. It should do the trick.”
A black and white rendering of a man in smart clothes is shown. He is leaning calmly against a bar counter and holding a beer bottle. A slogan says: “Dignity. Learn how to keep it.”

Four women and one man are shown, each holding an alcoholic beverage. The man puts his arm flirtatiously around one of the women. She looks disgusted at him and the other three women watch disapprovingly. A slogan says: “Before you got wasted, you weren’t known as ‘The Creep’”

A woman is sitting crying on the ground surrounded by other people holding alcoholic beverages and in front of a table with alcoholic beverages and snacks on it. Someone is holding her arm and tries to pull her away. A slogan says: “A few drinks before, they thought you were fabulous.”

Five women and a man are standing around a pool table. Two women are holding alcoholic beverages and are engaged in a physical fight. The others watch in shock. A slogan reads: “‘But I was drunk’ doesn’t repair their friendship.”

A man is standing in the centre of the image surrounded by two women and a man who look at him disgustedly. The first man is holding an alcoholic beverage and has evidently wet himself. The following website is superimposed on the image: www.when-you’re-drunk-you’re-a-jerk.fi

A woman is standing bent over, holding her open purse in front of her face and throwing up into it. She is surrounded by other people. The following website is superimposed on the image: www.when-you’re-drunk-you’re-a-jerk.fi
A drawing of a glass is shown in the background. A slogan reads: “U think you can avoid a hangover. And you could. Two drinks ago. It takes LessThankUThink.org
A drawing of a beer hump is shown in the background. A slogan reads: “U think you’re the designated driver. And you were. Four drinks ago. It takes LessThankUThink.org
A drawing of a beer hump is shown in the background. A slogan reads: “U think you can make it to class tomorrow.”

A woman is lying on the ground. Only her legs are visible. She is wearing a short skirt and her legs are heavily bruised and dirty. Her shoes are lying next to her together with several alcohol bottles including a Jaegermeister bottle. A slogan reads: “You wouldn’t start a night like this. So why end it that way? Alcohol Know your limits”
A half empty glass of beer is standing on a window sill. A slogan reads: “Would you smash this in someone’s face?”

A car is standing parked on the side of the road. The passenger door is open. A slogan reads: “Would you get in with a man you’ve only just met? You wouldn’t start a night like this, so why end it that way? Alcohol know your limits”
The side of a street and a gutter are shown. A slogan reads: Would you squat down and pee into the gutter? You wouldn’t start a night like this, so why end it that way? Alcohol know your limits”
A woman is lying on the ground, bruised, dirty and either sleeping or unconscious. A slogan reads: “80% of pedestrian deaths on a Friday and Saturday night are alcohol related.”
A dirty public toilet is shown. A slogan reads: “Would you go to sleep in here? You wouldn’t start a night like this, so why end it that way? Alcohol know your limits”

Drawings of a superhero are shown, who is first climbing up high and then jumping down, head first. The last figure in the series is a normal person, not a super hero, lying on the ground unconscious. A slogan reads: “Too much alcohol makes you feel invincible when you’re most vulnerable.”

Three women are shown smiling and holding cocktails. In a second image, a dirty, sad-looking women is sitting on the pavement at the side of the road in a short dress. A slogan reads: “Don’t turn a night out into a nightmare.”

Three man are shown smiling and holding alcoholic drinks. In a second image, one of the men is lying unconscious and bleeding in front of a damaged car. A slogan reads: “Don’t turn a night out into a nightmare. Four Australians under 25 die due to alcohol related injuries in an average week.”

A woman is shown smiling and holding a beer. She is surrounded by others who are also holding alcoholic beverages. In a second image, the woman is lying on the ground, unconscious and bleeding after having fallen onto and through a glass table.  A slogan reads: “Don’t turn a night out into a nightmare. On average, 1 in 4 hospitalisations of people aged 15-24 happen because of alcohol.”

A man is lying on a stretcher with a neck brace, a bleeding nose and a blue eye. He is being put into an ambulance. A slogan reads: “Two drinks ago this wasn’t your ride. Excessive drinking is dangerous. Stop drinking while you’re still thinking.”

Looking through the windshield of a car from the driver’s perspective, we see a woman getting hit by the car. A slogan reads: “Just one more drink can hurt. Keep your friends from hurting themselves or others. Cut them off before they’ve had too much.
A woman is sitting bent over and possibly sleeping on a staircase outside. It is dark. A slogan reads: “Two drinks ago you could still get yourself home.”
A woman in a short dress is lying on the ground in the dark. She is either sleeping or unconscious. A slogan reads: “Bottoms up. Know when to say when”

A man is sitting in a hospital gown. Half his head has been shaved and we see a large surgical scar on his scalp. A slogan reads: “Six schooners, Five vodka lime sodas, Four rounds of shots, Two cleansing ales, One stupid fight, eight hours of surgery, thirty-two stitches, sixty days in hospital, ten months recovery.”
A drawing of a woman shows her crying surrounded by smiling and dancing people. She is holding a phone and is giving a thumbs up. A slogan reads: “Thanks Alcohol”

Two men are sitting sleeping and leaning against a tree in the dark on a busy street outside. They look desheveled and one of them has a wet t-shirt on. A slogan reads: “Binge drinking. What are you doing to yourself?”

A woman and a man are shown at a bar. The man is holding an alcoholic drink and is very clumsily attempting to kiss the woman. The man’s pants are wet and he looks highly intoxicated. The woman is pushing him away and is looking disgusted. Next to the two characters, the same man is depicted again, representing an earlier version of himself. He is standing at the bar, holding a drink and is watching the embarrassing situation unfold looking uncomfortable. A slogan reads: “Binge Drinking. What are you doing to yourself?”

A man in a sports jersey with bloody and bruised knuckles is aggressively pointing and shouting at a security guard. His arm is around an uncomfortable looking earlier version of himself. A slogan reads: “Binge drinking. What are you doing to yourself?”

A woman is lying on the pavement either sleeping or unconscious in a short dress with her underwear visible. A second woman, similarly dressed, is sitting next to her on the ground. A police officer with gloves is kneeling besides them. A slogan reads: “Binge Drinking. What are you doing to yourself?”

A woman in a short party dress is walking with her shows in her hands, a vacant expression, arms hanging, and looking disheveled. She has an open wound on her forehead and has a zombie-like appearance. A slogan reads: “Night of the reckless drunk. When you drink too much you lose control and put yourself at risk.”

Two women and two men are sitting at a table, each holding alcoholic drinks and laughing. Three of them are fully visible with a tag close to their head that informs the viewer about what happens to them later that night. The man’s tag says: “Aggro Drinker”. The women’s tags say “Vomiting by 10:30” and “Refused entry”, respectively. A general slogan reads: “What’s your relationship with alcohol? Find out more at: mydrinkingchoices.qld.gov.au"

A before and after image of a man’s face is presented. In the before version, the man is heavier and generally looks more unhealthy and disheveled than in the after image. Text on the image reads: “This is how you look after 28 days without alcohol.”
A woman is shown surrounded by others partying and dancing. She has a big smile on her face and is clearly enjoying the party. No alcohol is visible in the image.
Two man are sitting on a couch. One of them is sleeping or unconscious. The other is sitting next to him, posing for the picture and smiling with two thumbs up.
Two images of a woman are shown. She is lying in bed and looking dazed, sleepy and sick in one image and sleeping in the second.

A man is shown sleeping at the top of a staircase in the middle of a hallways in front of the entrance door to an apartment. His upper body is naked. He is wearing only shoes, socks, and a mini skirt that seems to be part of a bee costume.
A man is shown sleeping on on public transport.
A woman is shown looking disheveled and generally groggy, wearing a bathrobe.

A woman and a man are lying on the ground sleeping with a blanket over them. A second woman who looks heavily intoxicated is posing for the picture, smiling and giving a thumbs up. In the background a group of people is sitting around snacks and bottles of alcohol.
A blurry image of a man lying on the ground looking highly intoxicated. His mouth is full of snacks with the snack package still win his hand.

A man is posing for the image with a note attached to his chest that reads: “I spilled my bear all over the bar”. He is looking away from the photographer with an annoyed/embarrassed look on his face.

Two man are depicted in a bathroom. One is leaning forward, facing away from the image and bracing himself against a wall. He may be about to throw up into the toilet. The second man is holding a bottle of alcohol up for the picture and is smiling into the camera giving a thumbs up.

A blurry picture of four people shows one person lying on a bathroom floor, possibly unconscious or highly intoxicated. A second person is kneeling over the first and a third and fourth are standing next to the two.
A woman is kneeling in front of a toilet, holding up an empty Prosecco glass, possibly throwing up into a toilet. A second woman is holding her hair.
A package of pain pills (Paracetamol) is held up for the image with two empty bottles of wine visible in the background.

A man is posing for the image with a note attached to his chest that reads: “I spilled my bear all over my friend’s purse”. He is looking at the photographer, flushed and smiling with a somewhat ebarrassed look on his face.
A man is hanging over a toilet bowl with his hand in front of his mouth.
A woman is kneeling on the pavement with her head on the ground. It is dark outside.
A woman is being held up by a man, hanging in his arms and evidently sleeping or unconscious. Her head is hanging back with her mouth open.
A man is lying on a bench that might be outdoor furniture of a bar or restaurant. His head is hanging off the bench and
A group of four women and two men are standing around a sleeping man who is lying on the ground. They are smiling and laughing in the camera.
Two men are lying on a couch in awkward positions looking disheveled and generally intoxicated. Both are holding beer bottles. One is sleeping, the other looks like he will fall asleep any second.

A man is lying on a couch sleeping with his head resting on the shoulder of a woman. The man’s button down shirt has been opened and his face and upper body are completely covered in drawings. The woman is smiling into the camera, posing for the picture and holding several pens. Text around the image reads: “Human colouring book. Available for all to enjoy. @theteamstruggle”
A man is lying unconscious or sleeping on a bathroom floor clutching the toilet seat with one hand. In front of him stands a water bottle.)

Michael from the US American show “the Office” is shown. He is grimacing, bearing his front teeth and furrowing his brows like he is very embarrassed about something. Text on the image reads: “my face when someone tells me what I did while I was drunk”

A man is depicted sitting in a room with several book shelves. He is looking calm but distraught away from from the camera and holding his face in his hands. Text around the image reads: “Something, um, not that chill happened last night @MyTherapistSays” and “When you have to confront your friend about last nights drunk behavior”
A collage of four small images shows a woman with sunglasses and a bloody scrape on her nose, a closeup of each of her elbows with bloody scrapes and a close up of her big toe which is also bloody.
A man is taking a selfie in a mirror, showing off his bloody and bruised elbow. He is making a sad face.

A woman is lying on the ground on her belly looking generally disheveled and holding a drink which has spilled on the ground beneath her. She is lying a meter away from a bike that has fallen on the ground and she has lost one of her shoes.
A closeup of a women’s left eye shows a bruised, very blue eyelid.

A collage of three images shows a woman with a neck brace and an IV in a hospital bad making a funny sad face, a closeup of the neck brace and another closeup of her neck without the brace with a large bruise
A collage of three images shows the bloody, bruised and scraped face of a woman from different angles. She looks disheveled and sad.

A collage of two images shows a before and after picture of a woman’s face. In one image she is shown with styled hair and make-up on. On the other image she is disheveled with unwashed hair and a large, bloody wound covering the entire left half of her face.
A man is lying on the floor of a hallway of what looks like a hotel or apartment building. His pants are half down and he appears to be sleeping.
A man is lying face-down in a large bush having evidently lost control and fallen in head first. His arms are down meaning he was not aware enough to catch his fall.
A woman is shown on a train standing in the path between the seats, bend over and holding an ice pack to her lower back. She is making a pained face.

A man is lying on his back next to an ATM and a casino game machine. His feet are awkwardly propped up against the wall and he is evidently sleeping or unconscious. A second man poses for the image next to the sleeping man making a funny face.

A man lies on his back sleeping in a bed. A closeup of his head is shown and we see a can of an alcoholic drink in the background. Around his head, an assortment of makeup is laid out. An elf puppet is sitting next to him and was made to look like it is holding and eye shadow pallet. The man’s face is completely covered in makeup including eye shadow and lip stick and his finger nails are painted.

A collage of two images is shown. In the first image, titled “Yoga master”, a woman is performing a back bend. In the second image, entitled “Jägermeister”, a man is lying bent over backwards on a park bench with his head and feet hanging on the ground. He is evidently sleeping or unconscious.
A man is hanging over a toilet bowl with his face directly over the bowl.
A woman is sleeping on a couch with her mouth open. Someone has balanced a large bottle of alcohol on her head.
A woman is dancing, looking happy and smiling and holding a Heineken beer bottle into the camera.

Two women and two men are depicted with their arms over each others shoulders. The two women are laughing heartily and holding Heineken beer bottles, with one of the men looking on smiling and the other taking a sip out of a bottle.
Two women and three men are sitting on a couch. Two of them are holding cocktails. The two women are in focus and are laughing and smiling happily.
Two cocktails with Bacardi branded straws and a large bottle of Bacardi are standing on a table.
Several people are dancing with one dancing, happy looking woman being depicted in the centre of the image. A man is holding two mixed alcoholic drinks
A close-up of a women’s lower body is shown. She is holding a large bottle of Bacardi.
Several people re standing outside with one woman dancing, smiling, and holding a mixed, Bacardi branded drink in her hand

A creative display of four taps is shown. The taps are attached to fruits (a watermelon, a pineapple, a coconut and a lemon) and a bottle of fruit flavoured Smirnoff is placed upside down into each fruit.
Three women are shown smiling and looking happy. One is holding a bottle and one a glass of Smirnoff branded drinks. One is putting on make-up, another holding a phone.
A bottle of Jack Daniel’s stands next to a bottle of Coca Cola and a mixed drink with a straw. Text on the image reads: “Jack & Coke Frozen”
A small bottle of Jack Daniel’s is being held up into the middle of the image in front of a busy city scene during the day.
A large group of people is sitting around a table, toasting one another enthusiastically with Patron branded glasses
A woman hugs a smiling man who is holding a large bottle of Jose Cuervo Tequila
Four glasses of mixed drinks are being held up for toasts over a table with snacks and a large bottle of Jose Cuervo Tequila
A laughing woman is pouring Jose Cuervo Tequila into glasses being held up by two other people. She is also holding a glass herself.
A cocktail glass is standing on a table. Text on the image reads: “The Cuervo Margarita”
A woman is holding up a blow up dinosaur that is about the same size as her and pretends to kiss it. Behind her stands a large bottle of Jose Cuervo Tequila on the ground.
Two women are dancing on a rooftop. One is holding a big red plastic cup, the other a large bottle of Jose Cuervo Tequila.
Two women and a man look serious, posing for the camera. The two women are holding small bottles of Jägermeister.
The torso of a man is shown. He poses for the picture holding a small bottle of Jägermeister.
A man holds a small shot glass up for the picture. In the blurred background, we see the man and two women, one of which holds up a large bottle of Jägermeister
A woman and a man look at each other laughing and toast each other with two shot glasses. (Version 1)
Two women and two man are standing posting for the picture. A woman is holding a small bottle of Jägermeister to her mouth. A man is holding up a second bottle for the picture.
A woman is sitting on the shoulders of a man who is holding two shot glasses. She is pouring Jägermeister into the glasses from a a large bottle, smiling.
A woman and a man are sitting on a bench outside surrounded by two other men who are only partially visible. They are smiling and toasting each other, each holding a small bottle of Jägermeister.

A woman is leaning against a man resting her head on his shoulder. They are both facing and posting for the camera. She is holding up a shot glass, which he pours Jägermeister into from a small bottle.

A man is sitting on the ground smiling and posing for the camera and holding up a large Jägermeister bottle. A woman and a second man stand beside him looking at him. The woman is holding up another Jägermeister bottle. (Version 1)
A large bottle of Sierra Tequila is standing on a table with a small sombrero as a bottle cap.
A man with a luchador mask is sitting at a small round table with several cans of Paloma Lemonade, a large bottle of Sierra Tequila and glasses with ice cubes and straws.

A man with sun glasses is sitting on a bench with a glass in his hand. Two women are sitting on either side of him. One is pouring Lemonade into the glass. The other is pouring Sierra Tequila from a large bottle into the same glass.
Two women are standing, smiling and embracing each other, each holding an Absolut Vodka branded glass with their eyes closed, possibly listening to music at a club.
A woman in a festive, fun, party outfit is laughing and pouring Absolut Vodka from a large bottle into a shot glass held up by someone else.
Two women covered in neon body paint are posing and holding up a large bottle of Absolut Vodka
A closeup of a woman’s hand is shown from behind holding a large bottle of Absolut Vodka. She is dressed in a festive party dress and in the background we see a smiling man waiting for her.
Two male, smiling bartenders are in the centre of the image pouring drinks into glasses. They are in a bar with many other people.
A man is smiling with his tounge between his teeth and holding two glasses with alcoholic beverages into the camera.
Four people are toasting each other with beer glasses.

A woman poses and smiles into the camera. In front of her are a bucket of ice cream, a jar of Nutella, a large bottle of Disaronno liqueur and a Starbucks cup with a mix of these ingredients. She has a straw between her teeth.
Three woman and two men are posing and smiling for a photo in front of a Christmas tree. Each person is holding an alcoholic beverage.
Two men and a woman are celebrating in a bar and posing for a photo smiling and making silly faces. Several bottles and glasses of alcohol are visible.
Several people are toasting each other with shot glasses. A woman with a broad smile is in the centre of the picture, holding a shot glass and a tray with more glasses.

Several people are partying on a boat, smiling, yelling, and dancing. In the front, a man is pouring vodka into the open mouth of a smiling woman, with others around them cheering her on. Most people are holding cups with alcoholic beverages.
A woman and three man are holding shot glasses and are posing for the picture, toasting towards the camera. They are in a bar.
Three men are sitting at a table, smiling into the camera. The table is littered with empty and half-full beer bottles and glasses.
Several people are sitting around a table, smiling and toasting each other.
Several men are sitting around a table toasting each other with large glasses of beer.
Two women are sitting on a couch posing for the photo, each holding a glass of prosecco.
Two women are posing for the picture, making funny faces and each holding a glass with an alcoholic drink.
Several people are sitting on the hood of a car. In the centre are three smiling women and a man who are posing for the picture and holding beer glasses.
A woman and a man are sitting at a table in a bar, posing for the picture. Each is holding a glass with an alcoholic drink to their mouth.
A large number of people are sitting around a table littered with beer bottles.

Five people are in the centre of the image. One is taking the picture with only their arm being visible which is holding a beer glass, toasting the four others who are facing the camera, each holding an alcoholic beverage and toasting the photographer. They are smiling and standing on a campground, possibly at a festival with other people surrounding them.
Two women are sitting at a table. Each woman has two glasses of alcoholic beverages with straws and each women has two straws in her mouth simultaneously. They are making funny faces at the camera.
A woman is surrounded by a lot of other people with alcoholic beverages, possibly at a party or club. She is holding a hose, likely used to consume a lot of alcohol very quickly,
A man is at the centre of the image. His mouth is wide open. A second man is pouring alcohol into his mouth. They are surrounded by many other people in a club.
Two men are sitting at a table in a bar, each holding a big pitcher of beer and drinking from it. There are additional cocktails standing on the table.
Two women are smiling into the camera. One is embracing the other, whereas the other is holding a large bottle of liquor.

A man is sitting in an arm chair, thoroughly enjoying a glass of brown liquor with his eyes closed. Text around the image reads: “After reading about the negative effects of drinking, I’ve decided to stop reading.”

A strip of two comic images is shown. In the first, a man is pouring red wine into a glass held by a women. He says to her: “Say when”. In the second image, the room is filled with wine so that both the men and the woman are immersed in wine up until their necks. She thinks: “When”
Two women are standing at a table smiling at each other. In front of them are three cocktail glasses
Four women are sitting next to each other smiling and laughing. Each is holding an alcoholic beverage.
A man is kneeling on one knee packing five big bottles of Smirnoff into a backpack. Behind him is a shelf with several more big bottles of liquor.
Seven men are posing, facing the camera, smiling and holding shot glasses.

A woman is standing in front of a home bar with a large number of liquor bottles. She is holding a large bottle in one hand and a glass in the other, which she is sipping from while smiling into the camera.
Four men are sitting at a table toasting each other with large beer glasses and facing the camera.
Two women are sitting at a table smiling. One is holding two white wine glasses. The other is holding one glass. In front of them is a table with two large wine bottles.
A man is standing outside, holding a small keg of beer and is drinking directly from the tab.
The right half of the lower body of a man is shown who is sitting on a couch and taking a bottle out of a cooler that contains two large Stoli Vodka bottles.
A large group of people is smiling and toasting each other with various glasses and cups. A woman in the front is holding a large Stoli Vodka bottle.
A woman is smiling into the camera and holding a small bucket with a straw and alcohol in it. She looks intoxicated and is surrounded by many other people partying.
Three women are sitting on a couch posing and smiling into the camera. One is holding an alcoholic beverage. There are several other beverages standing on the table in front of them.
A woman is sitting in front of a large cocktail glass, smiling.
Five women are smiling into the camera. One is holding a dog. The other four are holding a board with shots on it. In front of them is a table with lots of plastic cups.
A man is drinking from a large liquor bottle. He is standing in front of a shelf with lots of other liquor bottles.
A woman is posing for the camera at a club, holding a glass of alcohol.
A woman is standing with her head bent backwards and her mouth open. A second person is pouring alcohol in her mouth while a third woman is cheering her on.
A woman is sitting at a table with three shot glasses in front of her. She is smiling into the camera.
A woman and a man look at each other laughing and toast each other with two shot glasses. (Version 2)

A man is sitting on the ground smiling and posing for the camera and holding up a large Jägermeister bottle. A woman and a second man stand beside him looking at him. The woman is holding up another Jägermeister bottle. (Version 2) NOTE: This image is equal to pp45 and was accidentally tested twice in Study 1a/b
Two tattooed men with bare upper bodies, Sombreros and luchador masks are standing at a table. One is pouring from a large bottle into a Sierra Tequila branded glass held by the other.
